'''敘利亞-瑪蘭卡禮天主教克德基聖愛弗冷教區'''是一個[[東儀天主教|東儀天主教]][[教區|教區]]。<ref name="Vatican20191123">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 23.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/23/191123b.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191123164650/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/23/191123b.html |archivedate=2019-11-23 |language=en |date=2019-11-23}}</ref>

代牧區於2015年3月26日成立，負責牧養印度中部（馬哈拉施特拉、果亞、安得拉、泰倫加納全部，以及卡納塔克和泰米爾納德的一部分）的[[敘利亞-瑪蘭卡禮天主教會|敘利亞-瑪蘭卡禮]]教友，教座位於[[基爾凱埃|基爾凱埃]]。創立之時，宗座代牧區共有27個堂區和21位[[司鐸#羅馬天主教和東正教|司鐸]]。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 26.03.2015 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/03/26/0219/00492.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190724145708/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2015/03/26/0219/00492.html |archivedate=2019-07-24 |language=it |date=2015-03-26}}</ref>

宗座代牧區於2019年11月23日升格為教區，現任教區主教為{{link-de|多默·安多尼·瓦利雅維拉伊爾|Thomas Antonios Valiyavilayil}}。<ref name="Vatican20191123" />

